                <h1>Who Owns Claire's? Insights & Overview</h1>
                <p>Claire's is owned by Claire's Stores, Inc., which operates as a leading global retailer of accessories and jewelry for young women and girls. Originally founded in 1961 in Chicago, Illinois, Claire's has expanded its reach and now includes over 3,000 stores worldwide. The company focuses on fun fashion and self-expression.</p>
